title: Ron Funches
itunes:title: Ron Funches
description:
Actor, comedian, and writer Ron Funches is on Good For You to talk with Whitney about the art of podcasting, stand-up, and his wife's amazing ass.  We also hear about shrooming and tarot card readings.  You can catch Ron on his new Discovery+ show Chopped 420 and his podcast Gettin' Better with Ron Funches.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
